 use FP4 models.\n\n### Download svdq-fp4_r32-fluxmania-legacy.safetensors from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/spooknik/Fluxmania-SVDQ/resolve/main/svdq-fp4_r32-fluxmania-legacy.safetensors?download=true)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models` \n\nMore Info about the models [HERE](https://huggingface.co/spooknik/Fluxmania-SVDQ)\n\n---\n\n## 🟣Nunchaku Text Encoder Loader V2\n\n###  Download clip_l.safetensors from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/resolve/main/clip_l.safetensors?download=true)  \n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/clip`  \n\n###  Download t5xxl_fp8_e4m3fn_scaled.safetensors from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/resolve/main/t5xxl_fp8_e4m3fn_scaled.safetensors?download=true)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/clip`\n\nMore t5xxl models [HERE](https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/tree/main)\n\n---\n\n## 🟣 Load VAE\n\n### Download **ae.safetensor** vae model from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Lumina_Image_2.0_Repackaged/resolve/main/split_files/vae/ae.safetensors?download=true)  \n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/vae`  \n\n---\n\n## 🆙 Load Upscale Model  \n\n### Download **4xNomos2_hq_dat2** model from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Phips/4xNomos2_hq_dat2/resolve/main/4xNomos2_hq_dat2.safetensors?download=true)  \n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/upscale_models`\n\nRead more about the upscale model [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Phips/4xNomos2_hq_dat2)\n\n---\n\n## 🧩 Nodes Installed from Manager  \n\n- **rgthree-comfy**\n- **ComfyUI-nunchaku**\n- **ComfyUI-Easy-Use**\n- **Tiled Diffusion & VAE for ComfyUI**\n\n---\n\n## 📚 Resources  \n🎥 **Tutorials:** [Pixaroma YouTube Channel](https://www.youtube.com/@pixaroma)  \n💬 **Community Discord:** [Join Here](https://discord.com/invite/gggpkVgBf3)\n"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":233,"type":"Label (rgthree)","pos":[763.793701171875,475.6392517089844],"size":[243.486328125,30],"flags":{"allow_interact